      <title>曼谷豪华酒店氰化物致人神秘死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三初步尸检结果显示，在曼谷一家豪华酒店发现的六名外国人的尸体中检测到了氰化物痕迹，泰国警方称，罪犯据信就在死者之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</guid>
